      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA software (Ansys) used under documented quality management system with version control, regression testing, and change control procedures consistent with Gradation 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2021 R2 was operated under an ISO 9001-compliant QMS. Version control logs, regression test suite results, and release notes were reviewed and found compliant with Gradation 2 SQA requirements for a Medium model risk level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
