    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility is accepted at Medium assurance level. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is compensated by the strong performance of all computational verification factors, the high equivalency of inputs, and the quantitative output comparison results (all E/uval < 1.96, all percentage differences < 10%). The package conforms to ProfileMinimal; the digital signature workflow is pending and will be applied prior to regulatory submission. The hash field provides interim integrity verification.",
